{"tid":1844632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"切勿對支那人有任何同情之心","createTime":"2020-01-26T17:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T08:38:17.000Z","uid":12609,"like":112,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"ed21660fcdcf902afb5697cbbbdf11f59c71729c","tid":1844632,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"對住班支那賤種, 絕對唔需要有任何同情<br />\n靜靜地睇住佢地死全家就得<br />\n你對佢地同情, 等於對咁多手足殘忍<br />\n你諗下班賤種過去半年對香港人既冷嘲熱諷<br />\n被浮屍被失蹤被蛋姦被墜樓既手足<br />\n而家完全係現眼報<br />\n唔好同我講果0.00000001%既所謂&quot;清醒既大陸人&quot;<br />\n佢地有事就會話知黨既衰野<br />\n冇事咪又係跟黨走<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切勿對支那人有半點同情之心</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1697b2a4cd5aa58c8bdf05002bcb31c3eeac5483","tid":1844632,"uid":307203,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7msEag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7msEag.jpg&h=cb9ae09d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【武漢x香港】手足聯動，五大訴求，延燒大陸！ 就蔥友和香港手足聯合發起文宣戰倡議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d9bcd37d116fd3bd212113f3cbf91df48b0af24","tid":1844632,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e1be98092a05a391c2efafe79c75eef5fe2edc6","tid":1844632,"uid":206370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"自私人種"},{"pid":"2d1c3c6f4e4b227550ca021306b28d097e403b1a","tid":1844632,"uid":230642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ff814d38da63ff8fd57a86d7fb163cb7d874ec2","tid":1844632,"uid":223780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:18:08.000Z","msg":"佢哋班賤種啲命係命，被自殺被跳樓被浮屍嘅手足就唔喺命？<br />\n你哋同情班話手足係暴徒，虐殺強姦手足嘅仆街，對唔對得住陳彥霖同周梓樂？"},{"pid":"e888878f329703b08f8d6271da2c58d4be522